extendedInfo.description: Everything you want to know before, during and after the 2013 Oklahoma FFA State Convention held at the Cox Convention Center in downtown Oklahoma City, Oklahoma from April 30-May 1, 2013. Stay up-to-date on all information about the convention sessions, workshops, exhibitor hall, banquets, award winners, concert, state officer elections, downtown OKC information and more. Highlights include convention agenda, speaker bios, exhibitor hall details, state officer candidate information, push notifications, photos/videos from convention, etc. Learn more about the 87th Oklahoma FFA State Convention at http://www.okffa.org.App Keywords: FFA, Oklahoma FFA, Cox, Bricktown, OKC, Future, Farmers, America, convention, 2013, okffa
